    <p>{`We then walked around, tried to find a restaurant that ended up being closed, made our way to the Piazza Navona, `}{`*`}{`picture`}{`*`}{` `}{`*`}{`picture`}{`*`}{`, then the pantheon, more pictures, and then finally we went and found a place for dinner, Life Ristorante. It was good, more upscale than we have eaten at so far. We were very happy to rest our legs and eat a delicious meal. Though their portion sizes could have been bigger, it was still a great dinner.`}</p>
