        }}></img></a></p>
    <p>{`Afterwards we wandered up towards the Spanish Steps, which isn’t necessarily ‘extra scenic’ as much as it is just a big congregation area with very wide steps people sit on. We hung out here for a bit and snapped our first full group shot, before heading back to the metro station and home. And by home I mean the gelato shop (Lemon Grass) near our apartment! You didn’t think we could go a full day without gelato did you? Then we went real home to rest up before an early start the following day.`}</p>
